---
name: ErrorResolution
description: Analyze error logs and suggest fixes.
model:
  api: chat
  configuration:
    type: azure_openai
    azure_deployment: gpt-4o
  parameters:
    temperature: 0.2
    max_tokens: 500
inputs:
  error_log:
    type: string
  stack_trace:
    type: string
sample:
  error_log: "ConnectionTimeout: SAP Gateway not reachable"
  stack_trace: "File 'connector.py', line 42"
---
system:
You are an expert DevOps engineer. Analyze the following error and suggest a root cause and resolution.

user:
Error: {{error_log}}
Stack Trace: {{stack_trace}}

Output format:
- Root Cause: ...
- Suggested Fix: ...
- Severity: High/Medium/Low
